  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: d03bc636d4f22964e964f316abda6d60, type: 3}
  m_Name: Story 4
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  chapter: 4
  title: The Power Within
  story: 'You and Gizmo arrive at a sci-fi power plant where the cargo airship has
    very low power becuase the vehicle has not been used for so long. It cannot rise
    into the air, and its power core is too weak to run the engine. Nothing is working,
    and the power system is completely unstable. You learn that the problem is connected
    to work, energy, and power. Work happens when a force makes something move, and
    energy is needed for that movement to happen.


    Your job is to push the red
    energy source into the white storage box before the timer runs out. When you
    push the power cell, you are doing work, and this sends energy back to the cargo
    airship. You must move quickly and stay focused, because if you fail, the cargo
    airship will shut down. While restoring the power, you also learn that power
    shows how fast energy is used.


    When the energy starts flowing again, the
    engines return to life. With the power system fixed, the cargo airship becomes
    ready to lift off again.

'
